= VTN API =
The VTN API module is a sub component of the [[OpenDaylight_Virtual_Tenant_Network_(VTN):VTN_Coordinator|VTN coordinator]] and provides the north bound REST API interface for VTN applications
It consists of two subcomponents
:*[[#Web_Server|Web Server]]
:*[[#VTN_Service_Java_API_library|VTN Service Java API library]]

